<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
'''VRCat''' is the official mascot of [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]], a spacefaring orange cat with white markings. He wears a box on his head, with the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] symbol on the side.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Appearances ==
VRCat's first appearance was [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-MKanCkDck Introducing VRChat Plus] and has been seen in numerous official VRChat announcements and social media posts since.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
VRCat appears as the Early Supporter [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]] for users who bought [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] when it was first released. The badge can be pet on a user's profile on the website.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Dialogue ==
</div>

